{"tid":1894597,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【藍絲文字獄】孔聖堂副校被質疑 post「黑警死全家」藏頭詩 遭即時停職","createTime":"2020-02-24T04:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T15:23:08.000Z","uid":96894,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a33682d5a9ba714862f29a1b0c2ba70d102aabd9","tid":1894597,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2NLwnH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2NLwnH.jpg&h=6f5c6e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUs32ux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUs32ux.png&h=b247819b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只許克警辱民，不許百姓諷警；幾乎每天在社交網站辱罵市民是曱甴的警察，在過去大半年沒有一位受紀律聆訊和法律制裁，更遑論停職，卻有不少市民在網上諷警後，被撐警藍絲篤灰，甚至被停職。近日有藍絲「篤灰」，稱跑馬地孔聖堂中學署理副校長何栢欣在個人facebook賬戶，張貼表明撐警、實質暗諷「黑警死全家，一個都不能少」的藏頭詩。孔聖堂中學校董會未審先判，在今日（24日）凌晨發聲明稱，決定由今日起暫停何副校的職務，直至校董會成立的專責調查小組完成報告。<br />\n<br />\n早前一名48歲防暴警確診感染可致命的武漢肺炎，而他在病毒潛伏期更「密切接觸」85名同事。大批網民紛紛開香檳慶賀，坦言這是警察的報應。何副校在私人facebook轉載一則廣傳的帖文，呼籲大家不要落井下石：「黑心唔係咁好，警察都係打份工，死咗又幫到件事幾多呀？全部人齊心抗疫先有用，家人嘅支持都好緊要。一個確診啫，個個都開心到要開香檳。都唔明而家啲人點解會咁，不如諗吓點令香港好番啦。能否畀少少人性呀？少少嘢就大驚小怪。」<br />\n<br />\n一位名為Terrence Chan的藍絲在facebook指控何的帖文表明撐警，實質是暗諷「黑警死全家，一個都不能少」的藏頭詩，更上載何的facebook截圖，包括何與妻兒的合照，但並無遮蓋他們的容貌。這位藍絲聲稱何除是副校，也是聖約翰救傷隊監督，批評他「枉為人師、枉為人父母、枉為救傷隊長官」；又聲稱何的父親是民主黨前區議員何偉途，辱罵他「臭罌出臭草」，呼籲一眾藍絲廣傳、「齊齊推爆佢」，更稱「又要由（警察）員佐級（散仔）協會出手，去信孔聖堂中學及教育局投訴」。<br />\n<br />\n何副校的個人facebook帖文，明顯是私人言論，不過校董會的聲明以大篇幅與其「劃清界線」；一方面稱對方以個人名義發文，另一方面卻矛盾地、煞有介事批評何發表私人帖文前，「未曾知會」該會，亦「未尋求」該會許可，又謂孔聖堂中學及其校董會「一直堅守政治中立，反對暴力及任何違法」。雖然校董會一方面稱已成立專責調查小組，查明此事的來龍去脈，另一方面卻未審先判，即時停止何的職務。此聲明在短短數小時激起網民群起反對，「嬲嬲」破萬。大批網民留言批評校方以言入罪，對何副校施以文字獄。<br />\n<br />\n何副校facebook帖文<br />\n<br />\n黑心唔係咁好<br />\n警察都係打份工<br />\n死咗又幫到件事幾多呀？<br />\n全部人齊心抗疫先有用<br />\n家人嘅支持都好緊要<br />\n<br />\n一個確診啫<br />\n個個都開心到要開香檳<br />\n都唔明而家啲人點解會咁<br />\n不如諗吓點令香港好番啦<br />\n能否畀少少人性呀<br />\n少少嘢就大驚小怪<br />\n<br />\n#明嘅就明<br />\n#認同請轉發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b207fc8ebf17f093cc0322ff63f912cab7c766","tid":1894597,"uid":96894,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"孔孟儒學傳統優良<br />\n聖言之書世人授受<br />\n堂堂儀表非凡卓越<br />\n校務管理教界翹楚<br />\n董仲舒之再世還陽<br />\n無後來者前無古人<br />\n恥食周栗風骨傲雪<br />\n舐讀情深飲水思源<br />\n共濟同舟社會之福<br />\n狗吠非主一身正氣"},{"pid":"ee27d576ae8548a1d132ba3cdd40dd45f0609b17","tid":1894597,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:03:05.000Z","msg":"藍雪寶老師上星期五在銅鑼灣挑釁市民同市民打交路德會救主學校就唔駛停職，孔聖堂何副校批評黑警就遭即時停職 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ukVVRSqde3Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FukVVRSqde3Q&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAqdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=ba03746b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ukVVRSqde3Q</a>"},{"pid":"bde929e859af9324649a7e9e346a71c5643520df","tid":1894597,"uid":127067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"咁有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既然係個人行為 私人言論 同學校無關<br />\n咁點解學校又要出聲明 又要停職"},{"pid":"65239583025c6add28a400b58cb0f0a6447344ed","tid":1894597,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"你又唔係佢心入面條蟲<br />\n點知佢唔係真心撐警<br />\n副校俾黃屍呃左姐"},{"pid":"ebbd3126309e935e13699399ce10379baf7af4e1","tid":1894597,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde929e859af9324649a7e9e346a71c5643520df","tid":1894597,"uid":127067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"咁有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既然係個人行為 私人言論 同學校無關<br />\n咁點解學校又要出聲明 又要停職"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"孔聖堂中學：『政治不進校門，要政治中立』<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cad9bd5810248635c3e4228f48fe6c3278ce7f","tid":1894597,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:25:45.000Z","msg":"去佢學校集會"},{"pid":"53c4449301119f7358ff0d02c8faa12fd16f3160","tid":1894597,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"7350715c483bc157a473994faba36ddb99f0bf6f","tid":1894597,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n香港就黎要進入文字獄時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d156cbbe634797360b1164d1e7ffe39a26441e2","tid":1894597,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"即刻講返句<br />\n支持成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n還警察清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7c89d193a323feb3f22359a77b55dd57419ae8","tid":1894597,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"要推 煲大佢"},{"pid":"d3301e1905289dc72cbd9228600fa16902c8d5f0","tid":1894597,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"頂竟然冇人講"},{"pid":"c8b1f8a7d8818c7779cd3feb4f76b63d0be15cd9","tid":1894597,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d7c89d193a323feb3f22359a77b55dd57419ae8","tid":1894597,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"要推 煲大佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAxSXxH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAxSXxH.jpg&h=c90b93c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民Terrence Chan在facebook指控孔聖堂副校的帖文表明撐警，實質是暗諷「黑警死全家，一個都不能少」的藏頭詩，更上載副校的facebook截圖，包括何與妻兒的合照，但並無遮蓋他們的容貌。<br />\n<br />\n一眾連登仔即化身偵探，對比照片等公開資料後，發現這位篤灰網民其實是男警陳耀華。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>孔聖堂事件篤灰藍屍 terrence chan 地址已流出</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1894529/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1894529/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"37023f8c06e3ebfd5fc8ae127c00893809af1776","tid":1894597,"uid":73033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=29gcyCfco-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D29gcyCfco-s&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAqdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=05e64830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=29gcyCfco-s</a><br />\n<br />\n學校YouTube Channel"},{"pid":"008822f4ba3e36945a704f2f1bf0220d1956fcc7","tid":1894597,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"孔聖堂都要親支"},{"pid":"8ae4d71e15b75e5628fc42c039d595fe6dd83e77","tid":1894597,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7f1304b4d0120a7fd595f9aac07565dd069534","tid":1894597,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008822f4ba3e36945a704f2f1bf0220d1956fcc7","tid":1894597,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"孔聖堂都要親支"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"香港孔聖堂中學 郭少棠校監/楊永漢校長道鑒：<br />\n<br />\n我們為孔聖堂中學一眾舊生，有鑒近日母校發佈聲明稱有關何栢欣老師於私人社交媒體發佈貼文引致被停職待查一事，香港已正值多事之秋，此事已引起公眾關注以及引起爭議，故特此致函要求母校停止自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n我校創校於民國初年，當時香港政局動蕩不安，為弘揚儒學，為社會栽培棟樑之才，推動平等法律以及正面風氣。因此，當時曾富先生和簡孔昭先生創下孔聖堂。八十多年來抱著有教無類精神，一直為社會不遺餘力，興學育才。<br />\n<br />\n對於何栢欣副校長被停職待查，我等深表遺憾。因此事實屬個人於社交媒體之私人言論，突然被公開披露更被大造文章，引起社會對我校爭議。<br />\n此事無疑為有心之人對我校事務之惡意中傷，閣下應克盡職守，擁護學術自由並捍衛言論自由之精神捍衛我校。若我校執意反其道而行之，執意對何副校長進行停職審查等處分。實招人話柄，坐實自我政治審查及以言入罪之嫌，成為學界一大笑話。<br />\n<br />\n於我等看來，莫論政治立場。學校乃學子承教之地，不容政治此等大染缸染污，請閣下秉持學者應有風骨，保護我校師生表達意見之自由。<br />\n「孝、悌、忠、信、禮、義、廉、恥」八德為我校校訓，還望閣下莫望先人創校初心，萬不可讓事情再度發酵，讓各界對我校繼續因指責謾罵影響校譽，令各舊生恥與為伍。<br />\n是次修函，為敦促我校不應對何副校長紀錄處分，不可事後對其秋後算賬。應保持公開持平開放態度處理該事，勿讓此事為學界首開先河遺臭萬年。<br />\n<br />\n香港孔聖堂中學眾舊生<br />\n二零二零年二月二十四日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%94%E8%81%96%E5%A0%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%94%E8%81%96%E5%A0%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%88%8A%E7%94%9F%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%A1-%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1?recruiter=970306188&amp;recruited_by_id=6ca3ae50-8d05-11e9-8cec-c9c6efc3803b&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=petition_dashboard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AD%2594%25E8%2581%2596%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AD%2594%25E8%2581%2596%25E5%25A0%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2588%258A%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%3Frecruiter%3D970306188%26recruited_by_id%3D6ca3ae50-8d05-11e9-8cec-c9c6efc3803b%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dpetition_dashboard&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAqdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=703019a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%94%E8%81%96%E5%A0%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%94%E8%81%96%E5%A0%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%88%8A%E7%94%9F%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%A1-%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1?recruiter=970306188&amp;recruited_by_id=6ca3ae50-8d05-11e9-8cec-c9c6efc3803b&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=petition_dashboard</a>"},{"pid":"9aac51a09454e9edf1368e46671123235e2db3ca","tid":1894597,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:13:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"450cd73695ba3167f2c7617352d925168bc8c359","tid":1894597,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"謠佢老母，黑警死全家"}],"pinned":{"pid":"79b207fc8ebf17f093cc0322ff63f912cab7c766","tid":1894597,"uid":96894,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"孔孟儒學傳統優良<br />\n聖言之書世人授受<br />\n堂堂儀表非凡卓越<br />\n校務管理教界翹楚<br />\n董仲舒之再世還陽<br />\n無後來者前無古人<br />\n恥食周栗風骨傲雪<br />\n舐讀情深飲水思源<br />\n共濟同舟社會之福<br />\n狗吠非主一身正氣"}}